request.description:
Adds a new school to the database. 

**Expected Success Response (201 Created):**
```json
{
    "message": "School added successfully!",
    "schoolId": 1
}
```

**Expected Error Response (400 Bad Request):**
```json
{
    "errors": [
        {
            "type": "field",
            "msg": "A valid latitude (-90 to 90) is required.",
            "path": "latitude",
            "location": "body"
        }
    ]
}
```
